styleCard.description: An epic folk ballad with Arabic instrumentation capturing the journey through Saudi Arabian roads

directions: Start at Al Nisaay Street, Al Kharj, 16439
Go south on شارع النسائي (Shari' al-Nisa'i) toward طريق الملك سلمان
Bear right on طريق الملك سلمان (Tareeq al-Malik Salman)
Bear right on طريق الأمير سلطان بن عبد العزيز (Tareeq al-'Ameer Sultan Bin Abd al-Azeez)
Turn left on طريق الأمير سلطان بن عبد العزيز, then turn right on طريق الأمير سلطان بن عبد العزيز
Continue through Saudi Arabia toward destination...

composition.style: theatrical, grandiose, humorous Arabic folk ballad
composition.vocals: clear lyrics sung in local dialect
composition.theme: cheesy tourist music, over-the-top travel anthem
